<!-- SECTION 8A: ELIGIBILITY -->
<section class="content-section" id="eligibility-section">
    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="text-content">
            <h2 class="section-title">Eligibility for a Rural &amp; Tier-3 IMF</h2>
            <div class="content-text">
                <p>Eligibility for an IMF is set nationally by IRDAI and applies the same in rural, Tier-3 and metro locations. The concessions below are what make a small-town setup near Pune viable.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Entity type:</strong> Must be a Company, LLP or Co-operative Society, with "Insurance Marketing Firm" or "IMF" in the registered name.</li>
